    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine balls are cooking, boil a full kettle</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> remaining chopped onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
