      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>dried oregano </strong>and cook for 1 min further until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and<strong> vegetable stock </strong>with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until reduced to a thick consistency – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
