      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce thickens, add the <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>linguine</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>linguine </strong>and stir through a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p>",
